Privacy Policy for LumiFix
Effective Date: Oct 10, 2025

Contact Email: cangmut@outlook.com

1. Information We Collect
We may collect the following types of information:

Uploaded Photos: When you use the photo repair or colorization feature, we temporarily upload your selected photo to our secure servers for processing.
Device Information: Basic technical information such as device type, OS version, and crash logs may be collected to improve app performance.
Usage Data: We collect anonymized data to understand how users interact with the app features.
We do not collect personal information such as your name, address, or contact list.

2. How We Use Your Information
To process photo repair and enhancement features (via third-party API)
To improve app performance and user experience
To detect and fix technical issues
Uploaded photos are automatically deleted from our servers shortly after processing (usually within a few minutes).

3. Third-Party Services
Our app integrates with trusted third-party photo enhancement APIs (e.g., VanceAI). These services only receive the uploaded image data needed to perform the requested enhancement and do not retain your data for any other purpose.

We recommend reviewing their VanceAI Privacy Policy for more details.

4. Data Retention
Uploaded photos: Deleted automatically after processing
Usage analytics and crash logs: Stored securely and used for app improvements
We do not sell or share your data with advertisers or other third parties.

5. Security
We take appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data, including encryption of transmitted images and secure API communication.

6. Childrenâ€™s Privacy
This app is not intended for children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal data from children.

7. Your Rights
You may request deletion of your data by contacting us at cangmut@outlook.com
You may stop using the app at any time to opt out of data collection
8. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy occasionally. Any changes will be posted within the app, and your continued use of the app constitutes your agreement to the updated policy.

